<h3>Bentley's Daily Schedule<h3>
<ol type="1">
<li>Go for a 20-minute walk or 3-mile run</li>
<li>Get a treat</li>
<li>Have breakfast</li>
<li>Sleep</li>
<li>Play with toys</li>
<li>Have another 20-minute walk</li>
<li>Have dinner</li>
<li>Sleep</li>
<li>Go outside one last time before bedtime</li>
<li>Sleep some more</li>
</ol>
